data.description: Southend Findlay! Vinyl-sided ranch featuring a primary suite with 2 full baths and a half bath in the basement. Effortless living with first-floor utility, while the finished basement boasts a chic bar and office area. Step outside to a fenced yard, and revel in the fully finished, heated two-car garage. Don't miss out—schedule your showing today!
